title: SHOCKING!! Jana Na Dil Se Door To Go Off Air!
text:
» SHOCKING!! Jana Na Dil Se Door To Go Off Air! SHOCKING!! Jana Na Dil Se Door To Go Off Air! Star Plus’ popular show Jana Na Dil Se Door that stars Shivani Surve, Vikram Singh Chauhan, Shashank Vyas and Smita Bansal may go off air soon! Published: Tuesday, March 28, 2017, 3:00   
Star Plus' popular show Jana Na Dil Se Door , although is not seen on the TRP charts, has a strong fan base. The lead characters are popular among the audiences. According to the latest reports, the show might go off air soon! Read on to know more and also check out the latest updates of the show... Why The Show Might Go Off Air? 
Apparently, the show might be pulled off-air by the channel. Reason is obviously low TRPs! Recently, the show took a leap and the makers promised to bring a new twist in the show. The Show Might Go Off Air In May! 
But, the show didn't manage to get the expected numbers. There are reports that the show might go off air in May! Vikram Singh Chauhan Unaware! 
When the lead actor of the show, Vikram Singh Chauhan was asked regarding the rumours of the show going off air, the actor said that he isn't aware of it. Vikram Said... 
He was quoted by an entertainment website as saying, "This is news to me. We haven't been told anything as of now." Ravish Upset With Suman 
Coming back to the show's story, as it is known Vividha has revealed about Suman's truth. After the major revelation, Ravish will be upset with his mother. He will be seen arguing with her as she takes the wrong route. Atharv Goes Missing! 
There are also reports that Atharv might go missing, again. As Bua too, goes missing, the family members feel that Bua might have kidnapped Atharv! Story So Far... In the previous episode, we saw how Suman shouts that Kajri had troubled her a lot, and now she will put an end to her story by performing a 'bali' on 'maha amavasya' night.On the other hand, the tantric asks Suman to get ready as Guddi was getting Atharv ( Vikram Singh Chauhan ) to her. But Guddi would have saved Atharv. Instead of Atharv, Guddi gets Vipul to the terrace.Suman will be ready to kill Madhav, but will be shocked to see Vipul instead of Atharv. The tantric asks Suman to go ahead and kill Madhav.The tantric asks Suman to push Madhav, but she will be hesitant. As we revealed earlier, instead of Suman, the tantric pushes Madhav, Atharv and Vividha rush to save Madhav. But at the right time, Atharv saves Madhav! Suman and the tantric will be shocked to see Athrav and Vividha together. Atharv will be shocked to see Vividha and Sujatha. The tantric will be none other than Chintu. On the other hand, Vividha will be shocked to see Kajri alive. Kajri might have revealed Suman's truth.Vividha reveals the entire truth (he is not Raghav and his mother is Sujatha) to Atharv, who will be shocked. She exposes Suman and Chintu as well.Stay locked to this space for the latest updates of the show... Other articles published on Mar 28, 2017 Please Wait while comments are loading...
